Prerequisites
Before you begin, ensure you have met the following requirements:

Node.js (v18.0.0 or higher) - Download Node.js
npm (v8.0.0 or higher) - Comes bundled with Node.js. Learn more about npm
MongoDB (v5.0.0 or higher) - Install MongoDB or use a cloud service like MongoDB Atlas
Git (optional, for version control and cloning the repository) - Download Git
Installation
Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/your-repository-name.git
Navigate to the project directory:
cd your-repository-name
